The paper discusses the application of machine learning techniques (PCA) to improve the performance of an artificial immune system algorithm (DCA) for classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The use of biometrics data for stress recognition of automobile drivers suggests a possible connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT) sub-categories.
